{"tid":2017832,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做人其實有咩意義？","createTime":"2020-05-15T09:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T02:28:46.000Z","uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3429be65f49b3f107a1966759bc8b6f63788dde7","tid":2017832,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"呢個問題好似永遠無答案...<br />\n但就係忍唔住會去諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be9a05639b234409d5283ef52a796109d338072","tid":2017832,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:40:39.000Z","msg":"有錢有意義"},{"pid":"cd941e1028d762d0d9f4bdaf3e9c17ef0c177373","tid":2017832,"uid":216776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3429be65f49b3f107a1966759bc8b6f63788dde7","tid":2017832,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"呢個問題好似永遠無答案...<br />\n但就係忍唔住會去諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"幫老世打工"},{"pid":"73f4817e676420122e67fbdfd09b3d6ba838901e","tid":2017832,"uid":242102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"本來冇意義<br />\n但係有人搵到樂趣<br />\n有人覺得無聊，自己搵搵下又真係搵到樂趣，<br />\n對他們來說，那份樂趣就是意義。<br />\n<br />\n也有人認為自己的三觀就是意義，<br />\n譬如侍奉父母，開枝散葉，拯救人類，實現自我。<br />\n<br />\n以上兩個例子，讓他們即使生活充滿種種不如意，也可以為之過下去。<br />\n<br />\n也有人天然感受不到，也找不到意義，哀莫大於心死。如果承擔責任太辛苦，嘗試去滿足自己吧。"},{"pid":"3f28a40af46d1c9b14f0e603962e8db286c96708","tid":2017832,"uid":219768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:19:24.000Z","msg":"食飯睡覺打丁丁"},{"pid":"60ee40226bf14c5bf2d456a24c3da536656a2ebc","tid":2017832,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T01:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8705d31929b7956296b602f433225a647286fdf","tid":2017832,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:28:46.000Z","msg":"要自己搵"}]}